<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-56-0539 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Soviet Union is one of the greatest gas and oil producers in the world.In this connection the article discusses some of the problems of gasand oil production in the Soviet Union, such as an increase of productionup to 1990, deterioration of geological and mining conditions in theoil and gas fields, necessary improvements for exploration and productiondrilling equipment and the construction of new large gas and oil pipelinesfrom the eastern parts to the western border of the country. (MOS).</TEXT></DOC>